Server.NetworkInterface.Communication

Class BaseCommunication

  • java.lang.Object
    • Server.NetworkInterface.Communication.BaseCommunication
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FakeCommunication, RMICommunication, SocketCommunication

    public abstract class BaseCommunication
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is designed to abstract the communication. In this way we can have methods in common between client connected in RMI and Socket connected with the implementation of this class. Created by Emanuele on 09/05/2016.
